@host = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@chatID = 766
@displayName = Cheap Housing Collective
@messageID = 157973
@phrase = 🟩
@since = 2026-04-27T00:00:00Z
@until = 2026-04-29T00:00:00Z

### Health
GET {{host}}/healthz

### Count rows in Apple's message table
GET {{host}}/api/messages/count

### Local index status
GET {{host}}/api/index/status

### Local index text-source stats
GET {{host}}/api/index/stats

### Sync new messages into the local plain-text index
POST {{host}}/api/index/sync

### Rebuild the local plain-text index from scratch
POST {{host}}/api/index/rebuild

### Most recent 5 indexed messages
GET {{host}}/api/messages/recent

### Most recent N indexed messages
GET {{host}}/api/messages/recent?limit=10

### Conversations/chats for agent identity resolution
GET {{host}}/api/chats?limit=25

### Find a conversation by display name, chat identifier, or participant handle
GET {{host}}/api/chats?query={{displayName}}&limit=25

### Conversation summary by stable chat ID
GET {{host}}/api/chats/{{chatID}}/summary

### Messages in one conversation by stable chat ID
GET {{host}}/api/chats/{{chatID}}/messages?limit=50

### Messages in one conversation before an ISO-8601 timestamp
GET {{host}}/api/chats/{{chatID}}/messages?limit=50&before={{until}}

### Participants/handles for agent identity resolution
GET {{host}}/api/participants?limit=25

### Find participants by phone or email fragment
GET {{host}}/api/participants?query=614&limit=25

### Indexed messages with a person, number, email, or chat display name
GET {{host}}/api/messages?with={{displayName}}&limit=50

### Fetch one message by ID
GET {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageID}}

### Fetch surrounding conversation context for one message
GET {{host}}/api/messages/{{messageID}}/context?before=10&after=10

### Timeline across all chats
GET {{host}}/api/timeline?since={{since}}&until={{until}}&limit=100

### Search decoded/indexed message text
GET {{host}}/api/search?query={{phrase}}&limit=50

### Search decoded/indexed message text with a person, number, email, or chat display name
GET {{host}}/api/search?query={{phrase}}&with={{displayName}}&limit=50

### Next page of search results
GET {{host}}/api/search?query={{phrase}}&limit=50&offset=50
